data.description: Welcome to this beautiful townhome at Aviare of Montecito in Otay Ranch. This home has been greatly cared for and is primely located near the Greenbelt. As you step up to the second level you are greeted by an open-concept living room, dining area, and nice sized patio to enjoy your morning coffee or wine down in the evenings. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops, all stainless steel appliances, rich wood cabinets, and pantry. New carpet and paint throughout. The second level also has a primary suite with walk-in closet and large bathroom, an optional 3rd bed, and a half bath. Attached 1 car garage with a tankless water heater and 1 assigned parking space. Fantastic corner unit with amenities that include a large communal pool, spa, weight room, tennis and bocce ball courts, and clubhouse. Highly rated public and private school districts, biking and running trails and easy access to highways.
